  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the effects of cortisol on heroin craving and stress reaction in heroin
      addicted subjects Randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, cross-over, single
      administration of study medication Study hypothesis:Cortisol has an inhibiting effect on
      heroin craving and stress reactivity in opioid dependent subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
